graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[ModelMesh Controller<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "ModelMesh Runtime Pods"
        ModelMesh[ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC]
        RuntimeAdapter[Runtime Adapter<br/>Sidecar]
        RestProxy[REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional]
        ModelServer[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]

        RestProxy -->|translates to gRPC| ModelMesh
        ModelMesh -->|routes to| RuntimeAdapter
        RuntimeAdapter -->|manages| ModelServer
    end

    User[User/CLI] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]

    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| Deployment[Runtime Deployments]
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Service[ClusterIP Services]
    Controller -->|connects to| etcd[etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP<br/>Metadata Store]

    Deployment -->|deploys| ModelMesh

    ModelMesh -->|queries metadata| etcd
    RuntimeAdapter -->|downloads models| S3[S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    Client[Inference Client] -->|gRPC 8033| ModelMesh
    Client -->|HTTP 8008| RestProxy

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes 8443| Controller
    Prometheus -->|scrapes 2112| ModelMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style etcd fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
